OL,3,CDad denies murder of daughter, 14, as
OL,4,Ccharges against mum dropped
OL,6,FThe dad of a teenage girl who
OL,7,Fallegedly died in a stabbing has
OL,8,Fdenied murdering her.
OL,10,FSimon Vickers, 48, appeared at
OL,11,FTeesside Crown Court on Monday and
OL,12,Fpleaded not guilty to the murder of
OL,13,FScarlett Vickers. He also pleaded not
OL,14,Fguilty to a second charge of
OL,15,Fmanslaughter.
OL,17,FCharges against Scarlett's mum, Sarah
OL,18,FHall, have been dropped. Judge Francis
OL,19,FLaird told Ms Hall, 44, that she could
OL,20,Fleave the courtroom or stay and watch
OL,21,Fproceedings.
