OL,6,FScarlett Vickers died on Friday 5 July
OL,7,Fat her home on Geneva Road in
OL,8,FDarlington.
OL,10,FPolice and paramedics were called
OL,11,Fshortly after 11pm, but when they
OL,12,Farrived at the scene, the 14-year-old
OL,13,Fwas dead.
