OL,6,FJudge Laird told Simon Vickers, of
OL,7,FGeneva Road, that his trial will take
OL,8,Fplace on 2 October, adding: "You are
OL,9,Frequired, by law, to serve a document
OL,10,Fcalled a defence statement. This will
OL,11,Fset out your defence. Your lawyers
OL,12,Fwill write this on your behalf. You
OL,13,Fare remanded into custody."
OL,15,FScarlett was a year nine pupil at
OL,16,FHaughton Academy.
OL,18,FIn a tribute, the school said: "She
OL,19,Fwas always immaculately turned out,
OL,20,Frespectful and polite.
